{
  "info": {
    "name": "Medisy Import API",
    "description": "Collection untuk import data Medisy via Excel/CSV\n\nBase URL: http://localhost:3000\n\n⚠️ Postman Web Version tidak bisa akses localhost.\n   Gunakan: ngrok http 3000\n   lalu set base_url ke https://xxxx.ngrok-free.app",
